you try 13 weeks of hell

283
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,839
at Parris Island,
South Carolina,

284
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:03,838
and you'll find out
if you got what it takes.

285
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:07,077
You'll find out
if you really are a man,

286
