to questions.

295
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:33,876
So if any of you young men
do have questions,

296
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:36,155
go ahead
and raise your hands.

297
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:38,077
Come on, now.
Don't be afraid.

298
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:40,475
Don't forget, a good
Marine's a thinking Marine.

299
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:41,839
Billy Vorsovich, sir.

300
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:45,196
When would I get to wear
a uniform like you?

301
00:15:45,280 --> 00:15:48,272
You can be wearing this
in 13 weeks.

302
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:49,869
Go! Go!

303
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,552
Go, Massapequa!

304
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:53,949
Go! Go! Go!

305
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,718
- Yay!
- Yay!

306
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,509
Hi, Donna.

307
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:04,678
Go! Go!

308
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,278
Go, Massapequa!

309
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:07,469
Go!

310
