I want to do something
with my life.

329
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:52,835
I can get a degree in
business administration.

330
00:16:52,920 --> 00:16:55,036
You don't need
to serve your country?

331
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:57,833
Don't you care
about anybody but yourself?

332
