You can't stop them
by yourself.

339
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,757
Communism is
moving in everywhere.

340
00:17:11,840 --> 00:17:14,115
Where, Ronnie?
I don't see them.

341
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,513
They're not here
in Massapequa,

342
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:17,869
so I'll just take care
of number one.

343
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,837
That's right.
Me... Stevie, number one.

344
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,713
Someone's got to stay
with the women and children

345
00:17:22,760 --> 00:17:25,069
while the men
go do the fighting.

346
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:27,549
All I'm saying is,
think about it.

347
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,993
Think about it,
Ronnie.

348
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:31,753
Stevie, who are you taking
