She's a pretty girl
from Ronkonkoma.

357
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:47,873
What's her name?

358
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,069
You don't know her.

359
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,957
What's her name,
Ronnie?

360
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:52,359
Her name
is Lombardi.

361
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,316
Lombardi?

362
