Ronnie.

484
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:03,712
You're doing
the right thing.

485
00:23:03,760 --> 00:23:05,478
Communism has
to be stopped.

486
00:23:05,560 --> 00:23:07,755
It's God's will
you go.

487
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:09,319
We're proud of you.

488
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:10,913
Be careful,
that's all.

489
